Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:44.56,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 它随后移出了画面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.35,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,so we don't get to see anything more after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.35,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以在那之后我们没有看到更多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But actually if you just ping pong the frames near the landing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:52.20,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但实际上 如果你把落地附近的帧打成乒乓状
