Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.44,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,就像从7点钟的位置开始 进进出出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:05.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,There's black spots where the shadow of the heat shield is just before it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:05.58,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,隔热罩的影子在它落地前有一些黑点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It probably has zero scientific value knowing this but I thought it was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.78,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,知道这些可能没有科学价值 但我认为这很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,They have the Mars Reconnaissance Orbiter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们有火星勘测轨道器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.99,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and it was able to take images off the site the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.99,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它能够在第二天拍摄到该地点的图像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.71,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,showing the landing site of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.71,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,显示飞船的着陆点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:23.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,the spacecraft, the heat shield, the parachute, the aeroshell, the sky crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:23.36,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,航天器、隔热罩、降落伞、气囊、天车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,All that stuff was scattered out over the area over a few kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:27.34,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所有这些东西都散落在几公里的区域内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And during the landing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.72,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而在着陆过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:34.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,they actually slewed the camera on the Reconnaissance Orbiter over to higher angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:34.18,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们实际上把侦察轨道器上的摄像机转到了更高的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So that they could actually catch the landing live
