Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.75,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当然 火星勘测轨道飞行器采取的是条状的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,so this is part of a much larger image.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.94,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以这是一张更大的图像的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:52.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,There is the thing under the parachute there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:52.06,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,那里是降落伞下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:55.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But yeah down here this is actually where the landing occurred
