Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:19.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Stepping up a bit this is what the crater Gale Crater looks like from orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:19.28,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,再往上走一点 这是从轨道上看盖尔陨石坑的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And the Curiosity landed in the top left region here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.86,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,好奇号在这里的左上方区域着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.34,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,That's to the northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.34,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,那是在西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.70,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,You can see the big long black sand dune area there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.70,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以看到那里的大的长的黑色沙丘区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Zooming in a bit more,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.31,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,再放大一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:36.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,you can see the channel right in the top left, the channel that flows in from the north
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:36.60,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以看到左上方的通道 从北边流进来的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:41.19,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and beyond that channel you get an outflow area, a relatively flat area
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:41.19,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而在这个通道之外 你会看到一个流出的区域 一个相对平坦的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and on the left side of this dune area
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.86,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,在这个沙丘区的左侧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:49.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,you come to see a sort of gap where they plan to cross it onto Mount Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:49.40,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你会看到一个缺口 他们计划在那里穿越到夏普山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:57.11,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Okay so here we have a 3D model based upon satellite data from the Mars Reconnaissance Orbiter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:57.11,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,好的 所以这里我们有一个基于火星勘测轨道器的卫星数据的三维模型
