Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.14,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这显示了同一个着陆点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and you can see a lot of the same features that we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.76,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以看到很多与我们看到的相同的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,I mean obviously you see that dune area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.87,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 很明显 你看到了那个沙丘区
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.13,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,You can see these shorelines
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.13,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以看到这些海岸线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.16,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and actually if you slide this way you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.16,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,实际上 如果你这样滑动 你可以看到
