Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.56,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这显然是我向北滑行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is a channel that flowed into Gale Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.92,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是一条流入盖尔火山口的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It forms this alluvial flan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.28,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它形成了这个冲积板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:20.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So the landing site is roughly about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:20.27,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以着陆点大概在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:26.40,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And one thing you couldn't really tell from those cameras looking straight down was that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:26.40,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,有一件事你无法从那些相机上看出来 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,there's actually a lot of relief in the terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.36,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,地形中实际上有很多的浮雕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:34.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,If you look and I pan downwards you can actually see that to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:34.56,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果你看 我往下看 你实际上可以看到南部的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:39.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,On the other side of these sand dunes is quite a substantial mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:39.31,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,在这些沙丘的另一边是一座相当大的山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:43.99,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is about five kilometers tall fifteen thousand feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:43.99,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这大约有五公里高 一万五千英尺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:49.84,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And this is where Curiosity has been going for the last eight years or so
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:49.84,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这就是好奇号在过去八年左右的时间里一直在走的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:53.57,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,slowly making its way around these dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:53.57,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,慢慢地绕过这些沙丘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.02,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It basically headed down this way through this area here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.02,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它基本上是以这种方式穿过这个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:03.05,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It had made a number of diversions and it's going around this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:03.05,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它已经做了一些分流 它正在绕过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And going to be climbing up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.42,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,并将在这里爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:08.62,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And eventually hoping to head up here into that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:08.62,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,并最终希望从这里往上走 进入那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And as it goes up the side of this mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.82,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当它爬上这座山的一侧时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:16.20,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,you've got to realize that this is geology that's been laid down by sediment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:16.20,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你必须意识到这是由沉积物铺设的地质学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:22.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,so as you go up, you're going to younger and younger terrain features.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:22.31,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以当你往上走时 你会看到越来越年轻的地形特征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So you're getting a sort of a geological history of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.94,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以你会得到一种火星的地质历史
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.26,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And that's very good
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.26,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而这是非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:31.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,because it can help you reconstruct the geological history of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:31.86,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因为它可以帮助你重建这个星球的地质历史
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And this is what Curiosity sees of Mount Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.44,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这就是好奇号看到的夏普山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:39.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So it's a large mount in the middle of Gale Crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:39.87,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它是位于盖尔陨石坑中间的一个大山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.56,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It was formed during the impact
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.56,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它是在撞击过程中形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.14,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,when you have a large enough of energy large enough scales
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.14,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当你有足够大的能量和足够大的尺度时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.64,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,the ground actually behaves like a liquid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.64,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,地面实际上表现得像一个液体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:51.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and it rebounds a little during the crater forming process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:51.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它在火山口形成过程中会有一些反弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And that is what stood for billions of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.88,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这就是几十亿年来的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.80,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And so there's all this geology up the side of the mountain that we want to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.80,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因此 在山的一侧有所有这些地质 我们想要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But to get there they had to take a bit of a circuitous route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:02.88,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但是为了到达那里 他们不得不采取一个有点迂回的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:09.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,They had to initially go to the south west around all that black sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:09.68,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们最初不得不绕过那些黑沙 向西南方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:15.74,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So they could then turn and cut through a gap into the actual mountainous region.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:15.74,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这样他们就可以转弯 从一个缺口切入实际的山区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:22.47,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Now of course translating maps and images to an idea of what the Mars is like is hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:22.47,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当然 将地图和图像转化为对火星的概念是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,which is why I find it great that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.39,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我发现它很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:29.58,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,there's a few sites that NASA has gone and essentially constructed 3d environments for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:29.58,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,有几个地方 美国宇航局已经去了 并基本上构建了3D环境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is Dingle Gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.08,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是Dingle Gap
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Yes it's named after an Australian site. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:35.08,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,是的 它是以澳大利亚的一个地点命名的 你去那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.11,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And it's located where a bunch of sand dunes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.11,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它位于一堆沙丘的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So yeah this is all literally running in my browser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:41.60,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以是的 这都是在我的浏览器上运行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:46.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So I'm just dragging this around and lets me view various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:46.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以我只是拖动这个 让我查看各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.68,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,If you want to figure out say what this looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.68,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果你想弄清楚 比如说这个看起来像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.08,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,you just click on it puts a flag in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.08,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你只需点击它 就可以在里面插上一个旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:57.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And you can actually see where that corresponds to in the various navigation cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:57.77,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而你实际上可以看到这在各种导航相机中对应的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,They have a bunch of different sites in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.24,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们在这里有一堆不同的网站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It's not a huge number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这不是一个巨大的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.06,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,I guess it takes a lot of time to do all the photogrammetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.06,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我想这需要大量的时间来做所有的摄影测量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is a standing looking at this very interesting wall here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是一个站在这里看这个非常有趣的墙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.60,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And again you can just click on it and find the various parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.60,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,你可以再次点击它 找到各个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.92,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is the Kimberley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.92,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是金伯利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,These are all north office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.94,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这些都是北面的办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So if you look at the various points,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.77,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以如果你看一下各个点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.78,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,this is still north of the sand dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.78,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这仍然是沙丘的北部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:29.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,If I zoom out and over there is the sand dunes still getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:29.04,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果我放大 那边是沙丘 仍然妨碍着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But again click and you shall see the various images.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:33.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但再次点击 你将看到各种图像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,By 2018 they were had crossed the dunes and were starting to climb the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.46,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,到2018年 他们已经越过沙丘 开始爬山了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.31,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And one of the first things they did was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.31,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们首先做的一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:47.24,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,when they found a ridge they turned around and took a complete panorama
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:47.24,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当他们发现一个山脊时 他们转过身来 拍了一张完整的全景图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.94,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,which showed where they had been all the places they had analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.94,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这显示了他们曾经去过的所有地方 他们已经分析过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:55.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,All the sites they had drilled, photographed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:55.77,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所有他们钻探过的地方 拍下的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:01.48,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and subject to all the instruments that Mars Science Laboratory brought with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:01.48,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,以及火星科学实验室带来的所有仪器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And after seeing their opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,在看到他们的机会后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,they found a way to pick their way across the dunes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.95,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们找到了一条穿过沙丘的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:13.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,being always mindful of how spirit ended up stuck in a sand trap before ultimately failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:13.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,始终注意到精神是如何在最终失败之前陷入沙坑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:19.18,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Of course while crossing you've got some amazing photos of these sand dunes like the patterns there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:19.18,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,当然 在穿越的时候 你已经得到了这些沙丘的一些惊人的照片 比如那里的图案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Pretty darn unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.50,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,相当不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.07,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Teally glad that they actually include the scaling on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.07,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我很高兴他们真的在这里加入了缩放功能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:29.27,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,I mean this is what happens when you leave sand to get blown around and have all the dynamics work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:29.27,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 这就是当你让沙子被吹来吹去 并让所有的动态工作发生的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:36.42,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It's black basalt based sand which there may have been a whole lot more of this in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:36.42,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是以黑色玄武岩为基础的沙子 在过去可能有很多这样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:41.97,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,but even then you get these big dunes that are migrating across the bottom of the crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:41.97,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但即使如此 你也可以看到这些大沙丘在火山口的底部移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:49.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Now obviously Curiosity has been sciencing the heck out of everywhere as it traverses this landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:49.50,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,现在很明显 好奇号在穿越这一地貌时 已经对所有地方进行了科学考察
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:53.36,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And this image shows us all the sites that they took drill samples from
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:53.36,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这张图片向我们展示了他们采集钻探样本的所有地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.90,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and one thing I want you to notice is that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.90,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我想让你注意到的一件事是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.77,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,the names are all sort of appropriate to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.77,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我想让你注意的是 这些名字都是相互对应的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.14,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,so as they move down the themes are changing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.14,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以当他们向下移动时 主题也在变化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.29,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and right down the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.29,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而在底部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:07.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,those last two rows are all... once they cross the dunes onto Mount Sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:07.04,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,最后两行都是......一旦他们越过沙丘来到夏普山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,those are all places in Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.88,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这些都是苏格兰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:12.95,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So they have basically decided once they crossed on to Mount Sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:12.95,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以他们基本上已经决定一旦他们越过夏普山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:16.75,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,that is Scotland and they've been there for the last thousand days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:16.75,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,那就是苏格兰 他们已经在那里呆了一千天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.39,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,They're now crossing into a new region which is going to have a French theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.39,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们现在要穿越到一个新的地区 这个地区将有一个法国主题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.30,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And so for climbing Mount Sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.30,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,因此 为了攀登夏普山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.82,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,they're moving through a region right now which is called the clay unit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.82,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们现在正穿过一个区域 这个区域被称为粘土单元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:31.44,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,that's because it has spectra that implies there were clay minerals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:31.44,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是因为它的光谱意味着这里有粘土矿物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.88,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Very interesting if you're of course looking for ancient water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.88,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,如果你要寻找古代的水 那就非常有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.28,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,They're going to have to go up through this channel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:38.28,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,他们将不得不穿过这条通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:42.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,that has been cut down the side of the mountain through the sulphate unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:42.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,从山的一侧切入 穿过硫酸盐单元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:46.51,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Again the evidence from orbit points to high sulfate levels in these rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:46.51,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,来自轨道的证据再次表明这些岩石中的硫酸盐含量很高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.98,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But yeah this is a channel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.98,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但是 这是一个通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:55.04,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,that has been cut through it by a water flow from higher up Mount Sharp down the side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:55.04,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,被从夏普山更高处流下的水切割成的通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:59.46,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and so this is great because not only is it an easier path
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:59.46,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以这很好 因为它不仅是一个更容易的路径
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,but it also has cut down through the layers giving access to geology
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:03.72,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而且它还穿过了层层叠叠的岩石 使人们能够看到地质情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.50,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,which they might not be visible in other locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.50,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,在其他地方可能无法看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.76,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So as of right now this is the most recent panorama that's come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.76,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以到现在为止 这是最近下来的全景图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.87,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,This is from january and it's still in the Scottish region
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:14.87,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这是从1月开始的 它仍然在苏格兰地区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.25,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,but they're now moving headed into the french region of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.25,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但他们现在正向火星的法国地区前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:24.72,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,But the vehicle is powered by a radioisotope thermoelectric generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:24.72,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但该车是由放射性同位素热电发电机提供动力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.21,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,Its lifetime is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.21,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,它的寿命是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,The plutonium that powers that has a half-life of like 80 odd years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,为其提供动力的钚的半衰期为80年左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:35.23,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And as this power decays they're going to have to start taking steps to reduce the power usage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:35.23,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,随着这种动力的衰减 他们将不得不开始采取措施 减少动力的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,It's not just the RTG because that charges batteries
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.63,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是RTG 因为它为电池充电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.86,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,and the batteries also degrade over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.86,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而电池也会随着时间的推移而退化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.38,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,So they have to take all this into account
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.38,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,所以他们必须考虑到所有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,but most likely this thing is going to have a limited life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.63,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,但最有可能的是 这个东西将有一个有限的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.10,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,And it's really a question of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.10,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,而这实际上是一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.63,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,how far up it gets Mount Sharp before it has to take its leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.63,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,在它不得不离开之前 它在夏普山上走了多远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.00,1080P-sgbd-42,,0,0,0,,I'm Scott Manley. Fly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.00,1080P-shss-90,,0,0,0,,我是斯科特-曼利 飞行安全
